  <summary date="2019-08-26T18:01:21Z" status="Introduced in House">Restoring Oversight for Members of Congress Act

This bill requires agencies or managers that control access to federal facilities to provide immediate access to Members of Congress, excluding the Vice President, unless access is denied for national security reasons with congressional approval.</summary>
